set oven to 400
cook 
 - 400 g short pasta 
drain and reserve

set large pan on high 
add
 - olive oil 
 - 1 lbs ground pork 
cook on one side 
flip
add
 - 1 tsp salt 
 - 1 tsp garlic powder 
 - 1/2 tsp fennel seed ground
 - 1/4 tsp celery seeds 
finish cooking meat 
add
 - 28 oz canned whole tomatoes
 - 1 tsp basil
 - 1/8 tsp cayenne 
crush tomatoes
simmer covered until pasta is done 
stir in pasta 
put in a square pan 
top with 
 - 175 g grated mozzarella 
cover 
bake 10 minutes 
uncover 
broil on low for 4 minutes 

#pasta #weeknight #simple 

